Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.10,0:01:14.49,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}散发异样的情感 让我厌恶
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.61,0:01:19.88,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}你总是找着悲伤借口
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.88,0:01:23.28,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}扮演着女主角 让我憎恨
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.40,0:01:27.50,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}泪水根本不适合你吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.89,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A2F2&\blur5\3a&H24&\bord2}镜子里真正的我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.45,0:01:35.58,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}一事无成且原地踏步
